metadata.name: Star
metadata.description:
"Star" ⭐️ 

We all dreamed at least once in life, to be a star.
That’s what society want us to be inspired to.
This piece will invite to you to think about the “behind the scenes” of a star.
When the spotlight will abandoned you, and the lights will be turned off, what will happen? 

An eternal conflict between perdition and balance.
When the drop curtains will be closed, the temptations got the power, and here start the conflict.

Will you be able to resist to it? 

The top part of the star represents the balanced side. While in the sides of the star dominate the perdition.
